Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,伊奈里大人 fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.44,NOTE,,0,0,0,,我可以为你做任何事
